  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Your Patron grants you the following benefits for bringing down their enemies:</p><ul><li><p>When you deal damage to a <strong>Bloodied</strong> creature, you can spend <strong>1 Rest Point</strong> as a <strong>Reaction</strong> to regain <strong>2 HP</strong>.</p></li><li><p>When a creature drops to 0 HP or dies within 5 Spaces, you can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> as a <strong>Reaction</strong> to regain <strong>2 HP</strong>, provided the creature’s maximum HP is 5 or higher. You can only use this action once per creature per Combat.</p></li></ul>",
